subject: Golf
Masters Golf Tournament
lead_paragraph: Andy Sullivan of England easily won the Portugal Masters in Vilamoura after extending his lead to finish nine strokes ahead. Sullivan shot a five-under-par 66 to finish at 23-under 261.
